snippet.title: Air Hockey on Nintendo SWITCH
snippet.description:
Play Air Hockey and rediscover the fun and excitement  of this classic arcade game anywhere.

With stunning 3D graphics, you'll be transported straight back to the arcades of your youth.

Air Hockey takes full advantage of HD giving you stunning crisp graphics.

Play against another player in TWO player mode or against the smart artificial intelliget (Ai) player, but be warned winning won't come easy.
